{
  "stem": "4226.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we could put two in it to make it faster.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we started doing deals with, with the other groups.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For three buckets of raw potatoes, we gave them one bucket cooked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had the problem how to hide the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was a problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We, we, we couldn't hide them there, really.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The other German in, in the back, his deputy, was a very leftist fellow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had a French girlfriend with him who came from France on the-- whenever he, he met her.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he used to call me in and let me listen to London in the Hungarian language.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew the timing, roughly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he let me read the paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He, he was a socialist, but they didn't know, maybe even a communist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Germans didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was with us there until the, the fight for Berlin started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they mobilized all these Germans who were capable of still fighting, or half-invalids, and were sent off to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Never seen him after.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Can't remember his name, neither the other fellow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the, the, the other-- the other fellow from the Todt, as winter came, and the-- and the bombing were closer, intensified-- Munich got bombed in 14 days and nights in-- sometimes in July.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's the end of, of the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were taken out there on a special assignment after the third bombing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was to the-- to the Hauptbahnhof given a, a bomb crater in a rainy day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had the Krasna rabbi and another two with me to fill up the, the hole.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that rabbi-- and, and, and there were guards there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We couldn't-- we couldn't-- we were driven by Free French drivers-- so-called Free French.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
